Description: This field is used to record actors involved in the documented event.
This field is used to record the role played by the actors involved in the documented event.
This field is used to record objects known to have been used in the execution/performance of the documented event.
This field is used to record information objects that are known to have been used during the event.
This field is used to record documents that were generated as the result of an event.
This field is use to record any documented documents which describe the intended plan for execution of the event, as used in the event for coordinating its execution.
